    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained. The exterior shows some minor signs of age, such as small stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with regular use, but it still retains a respectable shine. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor scuffing on the door panels. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. It offers a great balance of performance and value for anyone looking for a well-kept pre-owned vehicle.",
