      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it's been well-loved and runs like a dream! Perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway. It\u2019s ready for its next adventure, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
