    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity during spirited cornering. The engine delivers linear power to its 8,000 RPM redline, aided by crisp individual throttle bodies. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are strong, featuring refreshed suspension bushings for precise turn-in. A well-sorted machine for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
